msgid ""
"Yahoo or AOL are examples of email providers with a :abbr:`DMARC (Domain-"
"based Message Authentication, Reporting, & Conformance)` policy set to "
"`p=reject`. Odoo strongly advises against using an *@yahoo.com* or "
